            "url": {
              "raw": "{{wsUrl}}/ws?quiz_id={{quizId}}&user_id={{userId}}&name=Alice",
              "host": ["{{wsUrl}}"],
              "path": ["ws"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "quiz_id", "value": "{{quizId}}" },
                { "key": "user_id", "value": "{{userId}}" },
                { "key": "name", "value": "Alice" }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Open this as a **WebSocket** request in Postman (New → WebSocket Request, or import recognizes the `ws://` URL).\n\nConnecting joins the session (the connection *is* the membership). Identity is the `user_id` query param (mocked auth).\n\n### Messages you SEND (client → server)\n```json\n{ \"type\": \"submit_answer\", \"payload\": { \"questionId\": \"Q1\", \"answer\": \"went\" } }\n```\nHost-only control messages (or use the REST lifecycle endpoints):\n```json\n{ \"type\": \"start\" }\n{ \"type\": \"advance\" }\n{ \"type\": \"end\" }\n```\n\n### Messages you RECEIVE (server → client)\n```json\n{ \"type\": \"join_confirmed\", \"payload\": { \"userId\": \"alice\", \"quizId\": \"QUIZ-...\", \"score\": 0 } }\n{ \"type\": \"user_joined\", \"payload\": { \"userId\": \"bob\", \"displayName\": \"Bob\", \"participantCount\": 2 } }\n{ \"type\": \"question\", \"payload\": { \"id\": \"Q1\", \"text\": \"...\", \"options\": [\"goed\",\"went\",\"gone\",\"going\"], \"order\": 1, \"timeLimitSeconds\": 30 } }\n{ \"type\": \"score_update\", \"payload\": { \"userId\": \"alice\", \"isCorrect\": true, \"awardedPoints\": 10, \"newScore\": 10 } }\n{ \"type\": \"leaderboard_update\", \"payload\": { \"entries\": [ { \"rank\": 1, \"userId\": \"alice\", \"displayName\": \"Alice\", \"score\": 10 } ] } }\n{ \"type\": \"error\", \"payload\": { \"code\": \"duplicate_answer\", \"message\": \"Answer already submitted for this question\" } }\n{ \"type\": \"quiz_ended\", \"payload\": { \"leaderboard\": [ { \"rank\": 1, \"userId\": \"alice\", \"score\": 10 } ] } }\n```\n\n### Covers (real-time scenarios)\n- Multiple users joining simultaneously; notifying existing participants\n- Question broadcast to all participants\n- Score update broadcast within 500ms\n- Leaderboard broadcast to all connected participants\n- Disconnect/reconnect (state preserved server-side)"
